"Поддерживается только в шаблонах: ``futuristic``."
msgstr ""
"Whether to show the category of the video library \"Package films\". Default"
" *true*. Only supported in the templates: ``futuristic``."

#: ../../source/portal_setup.rst:219
msgid "vod_show_purchased ``bool``"
